### 장바구니 상품 추가
POST http://localhost:8888/api/v1/cart
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 2
}

###

### 장바구니 상품 삭제
DELETE http://localhost:8888/api/v1/cart
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cartId": 1
}

###

### 장바구니 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:8888/api/v1/cart/list
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1
}
